        {
          "l": "গ", "m": 4,
          "q": "If \\(\\log_{10} 2 = 0.301\\) and \\(\\log_{10} 3 = 0.477\\), find \\(\\log_{10} 72\\). \\(\\log_{10} 72\\) নির্ণয় করো।",
